’."]},{"name":"Darensbourg","meanings":["Some characteristic forenames:  French Andre, Aurore, Camile, Pierre.","Altered form, under the French influence in LA, of German   Arensberg  . It is formed with the French preposition <i>de</i> ‘from’, spelled <i>d'</i> before a vowel. This surname is found mainly among African Americans.","History: The progenitor of many of the Darensbourgs was Karl Friedrich Arensberg, a German born in Stettin in Pomerania (today Szczecin in Poland), who arrived in LA in 1721. By 1724, Darensbourg, as he came to be known, was de facto leader of the German colony in LA."]}]},{"name":"Franco","type":"FIRST","attribution":"Dictionary of First Names © Patrick Hanks and Flavia Hodges 1990, 2003, 2006.","meanings":["Contracted form of   Francesco ."],"variants":[]}],"lifeSummary":"Franco von Arensberg was born in 1061 as the son of Ulrich van Arensberg. He had at least 1 son. He died in 1135, at the age of 74."},"et":{"1061–1135":"1061–1135","1089–1136":"1089–1136","1029–Male":"1029–Surnud","1029":"1029","1136":"1136","1135":"1135","1089":"1089","1061":"1061"},"fi":{"1061–1135":"1061–1135","1089–1136":"1089–1136","1029–Male":"1029–Kuollut","1029":"1029","1136":"1136","1135":"1135","1089":"1089","1061":"1061"},"fr":{"1061–1135":"1061–1135","1089–1136":"1089–1136","1029–Male":"1029–Décédé","1029":"1029","1136":"1136","1135":"1135","1089":"1089","1061":"1061","lifeSummary":"Franco von Arensberg est né en 1061, fils de Ulrich van Arensberg. Il a eu au moins 1 fils. Il est décédé en 1135, à l’âge de 74 ans."},"de":{"1061–1135":"1061–1135","1089–1136":"1089–1136","1029–Male":"1029–Verstorben","1029":"1029","1136":"1136","1135":"1135","1089":"1089","1061":"1061","lifeSummary":"Franco von Arensberg wurde 1061, als Sohn von Ulrich van Arensberg geboren. Er hatte mindestens 1 Sohn. Er starb 1135 im Alter von 74 Jahren."},"ht":{"1061–1135":"1061–1135","1089–1136":"1089–1136","1029–Male":"1029–Desede","1029":"1029","1136":"1136","1135":"1135","1089":"1089"